                     <interp inst="t18331017-156-off857" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18331017-156-off857" type="offenceSubcategory" value="receiving"></interp>
               feloniously receiving the same, well knowing them to have been stolen
